{"tid":530843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"耶撚宣布參選新東補選","createTime":"2018-01-16T07:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T07:54:00.000Z","uid":12362,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"42b245cf768a270c8f05e203e5c08467a8da897a","tid":530843,"uid":12362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T07:52:26.000Z","msg":"立場反同的性傾向條例家校關注組召集人黃偉明，今日向傳媒發出採訪通知，指其關注組成員趙佩玉將會參加新界東補選。<br />\n<br />\n黃偉明今日向傳媒發短訊，指趙佩玉將於明日下午三時半於立法會示威區宣佈參選，到時將會公布其參選心路歷程及政綱，邀請記者到場採訪。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，今次參選的趙佩玉曾多次參與關注組記者會等活動，反同立場明確。在去年11月她出席立法會的性別承認公聽會時，自稱是一位幼兒園老師、基督徒，同時是一位母親。<br />\n<br />\n她當日發言時，表明反對性別承認制度及變性手術，認為跨性別人士「就算切晒所有器官，終身打荷爾蒙，都不可能改變上帝的創造」。她又反對政府容許跨性別人士修改身分證性別，認為這是「虛假文件」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9B%BE%E6%98%8E%E8%A8%80%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%AE%8A%E6%80%A7-%E6%80%A7%E5%82%BE%E5%90%91%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%A0%A1%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1-%E5%B0%87%E5%87%BA%E6%88%B0%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%B1%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%2582%25BE%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E7%25B5%2584%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%25A3%259C%25E9%2581%25B8%2F&d=X9IW%2BGPfmw1%2FZ%2F0ymGgNcJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=d978c019\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%2582%25BE%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E7%25B5%2584%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%25A3%259C%25E9%2581%25B8%2F&h=d68d513d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9B%BE%E6%98%8E%E8%A8%80%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%AE%8A%E6%80%A7-%E6%80%A7%E5%82%BE%E5%90%91%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%A0%A1%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1-%E5%B0%87%E5%87%BA%E6%88%B0%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%B1%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8/</a>"},{"pid":"d3a8cd0fe57b83e0943fdbe643334b3eb1ccf690","tid":530843,"uid":12362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"個仔（黃之鋒）一邊砌，個老豆（黃偉明）一邊拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}